data.description: Like new split foyer home on a finished basement and large private lot. Enjoy the tranquility of this quiet and family friendly cul de sac. Spacious open floor plan, with separate dining room, large kitchen with breakfast bar, high ceilings, fireplace, and more. Master bedroom on main level offers vaulted ceiling, large walk in closet and double vanity. Finished basement includes large family room/media room, full bath, an additional bedroom and more space for storage. Come see it and you will want to call this place home.
